Quote: December is a glorious month of dietary amongst the natives on the coast ... The rivers, large or small, abound in eels, <i>hawera, upukuroro, haparu, patiki</i> and <i>parauki;</i> ... [fn] ... parauki is <i>Paraki</i> smelt (<i>Retropinna retropinna</i>).
